### Create a new form (Invalid Request - Missing TenantId)
POST {{FormBuilderAPI_HostAddress}}/api/forms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid Form",
  "fields": []
}

###

### Create a new form (Invalid Request - Empty Sections)
POST {{FormBuilderAPI_HostAddress}}/api/forms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid Form",
  "tenantId": 1,
  "fields": []
}

###

### Get a specific form by ID (Replace {id} with a valid form ID)
GET {{FormBuilderAPI_HostAddress}}/api/forms/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Submit a form response (Replace {formId} with a valid ID)
POST {{FormBuilderAPI_HostAddress}}/api/formsubmissions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "formId": 1,
  "data": "{ \"firstname\": \"John\", \"lastname\": \"Doe\" }"
}

###

### Get all form submissions
GET {{FormBuilderAPI_HostAddress}}/api/formsubmissions
Accept: application/json

###

### Test endpoint (Basic health check)
GET {{FormBuilderAPI_HostAddress}}/api/formsubmissions/test
Accept: application/json

